lead_paragraph: Southampton forward Jay Rodriguez says playing regular football again is the best feeling ever after suffering a two-year injury nightmare.    The 27-year-old believes he is in great physical shape ahead of Everton’s visit in the Premier League on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: I Want to Score in Every Game, Says Southampton's Rodriguez
